### POST

Registers a new Customer in the system.

+ Request (body)
    + Attributes
        - customer (Customer)

+ Response 200 (application/json)

        {
                "status": "ok",
                "customer": {
	                "id": 1,
	                "first_name": "...",
	                "last_name": "...",
	                "email": "...",
	                "status": "..."
